{"word":"H7077 - קָנַן - qânan - kaw-nan' - Make","slug":"H7077","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קָנַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qânan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kaw-nan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E0;&#x05DF; - qa&#x0302;nan</b> - <i>kaw-nan'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>erect</i>; but used only as denominative from <a href=\"#/H7064\">H7064</a>; to <i>nestle</i>, that is, <i>build</i> or <i>occupy</i> as a nest: - make . . . nest."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7064\">H7064</a>"}]}